# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-03-05 21:40

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:17
translate spanish ain_conversations_3e468446:

    # Z "So... are you ready to go where your [persistent.mom] suggested?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿estás lista para ir a donde tu [persistent.mom] sugirió?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:20
translate spanish ain_conversations_89e13ff5:

    # A "You mean the slave market she mentioned?"
    A "¿Te refieres al mercado de esclavos que ella mencionó?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:21
translate spanish ain_conversations_482745ab:

    # A "Of course! I will let her know that we're going!"
    A "¡Claro que sí! ¡Le haré saber que nos vamos!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:25
translate spanish ain_conversations_c6cf62ed:

    # "She jumps up and hurries off."
    "Se levanta de un salto y se va corriendo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:26
translate spanish ain_conversations_44bd9211:

    # Zt "That went fast..."
    Zt "Eso fue rápido..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:28
translate spanish ain_conversations_9d580c61:

    # "A while later... at the market..."
    "Un rato después... en el mercado..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:34
translate spanish ain_conversations_111a8bee:

    # Z "[A], I need you to go to the basement. You know the drill."
    Z "[A], necesito que vayas al sótano. Ya sabes cómo va."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:37
translate spanish ain_conversations_b53628af:

    # A "Okay, [persistent.dad]... but is there something I did wrong, again?"
    A "Vale, [persistent.dad]... pero ¿he hecho algo mal, otra vez?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:40
translate spanish ain_conversations_01c956fb:

    # Z "No. You know why. I will see you there soon."
    Z "No. Ya sabes por qué. Te veo allí dentro de nada."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:43
translate spanish ain_conversations_e50ef0e8:

    # "You leave the room as she prepares herself..."
    "Sales de la habitación mientras ella se prepara..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:47
translate spanish ain_conversations_289a209a:

    # Z "I have to leave for now."
    Z "Tengo que irme por ahora."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:50
translate spanish ain_conversations_969507bb:

    # A "Alrighty!"
    A "¡Está bien!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:63
translate spanish a_convi_1_18c06060:

    # A "Can I ask you for a favour?"
    A "¿Puedo pedirte un favor?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:64
translate spanish a_convi_1_3beb2044:

    # Z "Of course you can, short round."
    Z "Por supuesto que sí, pequeña."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:67
translate spanish a_convi_1_27826131:

    # A "I like it better when {i}you{/i} call me that. [S] is not always nice about it."
    A "Me gusta más cuando {i}tú{/i} me llamas así. [S] no siempre es agradable al respecto."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:70
translate spanish a_convi_1_918acffb:

    # Z "You have to admit you are kind of short."
    Z "Tienes que admitir que eres un poco bajita."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:73
translate spanish a_convi_1_ce963157:

    # A "Yes, and round in some places, I know, I know..."
    A "Sí, y redonda en algunos lugares, lo sé, lo sé..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:76
translate spanish a_convi_1_a3917bda:

    # Z "I'm sorry [A], I was just teasing you..."
    Z "Lo siento [A], sólo te estaba tomando el pelo..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:79
translate spanish a_convi_1_bc874a98:

    # A "It's ok [persistent.dad], I didn't mean to snap at you."
    A "No pasa nada [persistent.dad], no pretendía ser grosera contigo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:80
translate spanish a_convi_1_1672dc25:

    # A "I just... I guess I miss you."
    A "Yo sólo... supongo que te echo de menos."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:83
translate spanish a_convi_1_3cf11edf:

    # Z "What do you mean?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:86
translate spanish a_convi_1_a11f44f2:

    # A "We used to talk more, and to play together. Now you only look at me when you need me."
    A "Antes hablábamos más, y jugábamos juntos. Ahora sólo me miras cuando me necesitas."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:89
translate spanish a_convi_1_559fd68a:

    # Z "I have been very busy lately."
    Z "Últimamente he estado muy ocupado."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:92
translate spanish a_convi_1_d8d669c1:

    # A "Yes, but it's always with [S]. And with her, you also have conversations, you teach her things every day. All I get to do is be pretty and be available."
    A "Sí, pero siempre es con [S]. Y con ella también tienes conversaciones, le enseñas cosas todos los días. Lo único que consigo yo es ser bonita y estar disponible."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:93
translate spanish a_convi_1_830f52eb:

    # A "I like our games, and they're really fun, but it's a bit.."
    A "Me gustan nuestros juegos, y son muy divertidos, pero es un poco.."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:96
translate spanish a_convi_1_29bc6fef:

    # Z "Do you feel lonely?"
    Z "¿Te sientes sola?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:99
translate spanish a_convi_1_98578a9c:

    # A "That too, yes... especially in the last weeks. I..."
    A "Eso también, sí... especialmente en las últimas semanas. Yo..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:100
translate spanish a_convi_1_1c362c04:

    # A "I get bored, and miss you. [persistent.mom!c] is nice, but..."
    A "Me aburro y te echo de menos. [persistent.mom!c] es agradable, pero..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:103
translate spanish a_convi_1_6339f7ad:

    # A "Please, don't tell her this, I don't want to disappoint her."
    A "Por favor, no le digas esto, no quiero decepcionarla."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:106
translate spanish a_convi_1_f351f1d2:

    # Z "I understand what you mean, and yes, I guess I have neglected you for a while."
    Z "Entiendo lo que quieres decir, y sí, supongo que te he descuidado durante un tiempo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:109
translate spanish a_convi_1_3c03a56b:

    # A "...I'm sorry [persistent.dad]. I feel useless, but I don't want to be a burden."
    A "... Lo siento [persistent.dad]. Me siento inútil, pero no quiero ser una carga."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:112
translate spanish a_convi_1_4f35b135:

    # Z "Let's make a deal. You are needed by [persistent.mom!c] in these days, and I myself have several things to do..."
    Z "Hagamos un trato. En estos días te necesita [persistent.mom!c], y yo mismo tengo varias cosas que hacer..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:115
translate spanish a_convi_1_563045b5:

    # A "Yes, but..."
    A "Sí, pero..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:118
translate spanish a_convi_1_a0ae0ada:

    # Z "Let me finish..."
    Z "Déjame terminar..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:121
translate spanish a_convi_1_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:122
translate spanish a_convi_1_9aa4a31f:

    # Z "When we both have a full day or two where we don't have anything urgent to do, you and I will spend more time together."
    Z "Cuando ambos tengamos uno o dos días completos en los que no tengamos nada urgente que hacer, tú y yo pasaremos más tiempo juntos."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:125
translate spanish a_convi_1_9f2b424c:

    # Z "I promise that I will make time for us to do something nice that doesn't necessarily involve the things I've wanted from you lately."
    Z "Te prometo que sacaré tiempo para que hagamos algo agradable que no implique necesariamente las cosas que he querido de ti últimamente."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:128
translate spanish a_convi_1_1ded5273:

    # Z "We will spend some quality time together. And [S] or your [persistent.mom] will have nothing to do with it."
    Z "Pasaremos un tiempo de calidad juntos. Y [S] o tu [persistent.mom] no tendrán nada que ver."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:131
translate spanish a_convi_1_0289a220:

    # A "Yes, [persistent.dad]! Thank you!"
    A "¡Sí, [persistent.dad]! ¡Gracias!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:134
translate spanish a_convi_1_0e981d7d:

    # Z "I love you, little one, I don't want you to think otherwise."
    Z "Te quiero, pequeña, no quiero que pienses lo contrario."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:137
translate spanish a_convi_1_33a403b8:

    # A "I know you do, [persistent.dad], but it's nice to hear you say it."
    A "Sé que lo haces, [persistent.dad], pero es agradable oírte decirlo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:138
translate spanish a_convi_1_713f8e25:

    # A "I will do my best to do all my chores and lessons swiftly, and try not to disappoint you or [persistent.mom] ever again, I promise!"
    A "Me esforzaré por hacer todas mis tareas y lecciones con rapidez, e intentaré no decepcionaros a ti ni a [persistent.mom] nunca más, ¡te lo prometo!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:141
translate spanish a_convi_1_b3e3a7cc:

    # A "I don't even mind when I have to wear the collar anymore. I think I like it."
    A "Ya ni siquiera me importa tener que llevar el collar. Creo que me gusta."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:148
translate spanish a_convi_2_164b0edb:

    # A "[persistent.mom!c] told me a story about aunt Rabiah.."
    A "[persistent.mom!c] me contó una historia sobre la tía Rabiah.."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:151
translate spanish a_convi_2_a6ade7f5:

    # Z "And what story would that be?"
    Z "¿Y qué historia fue esa?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:154
translate spanish a_convi_2_a2e2275b:

    # A "She says she was your first girlfriend. Is that true, [persistent.dad]?"
    A "Dice que fue tu primera novia. ¿Es eso cierto, [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:158
translate spanish a_convi_2_9af51cbc:

    # Z "Ah, that story... well, it's not entirely true, but it is true that she was my girlfriend before your mother."
    Z "Ah, esa historia... bueno, no es del todo cierta, pero es verdad que fue mi novia antes que tu madre."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:160
translate spanish a_convi_2_42955788:

    # Z "Ah, that story... well, it's not entirely true, but it is true that she was my girlfriend before [W]."
    Z "Ah, esa historia... bueno, no es del todo cierta, pero sí es verdad que ella fue mi novia antes de [W]."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:164
translate spanish a_convi_2_f343c3fc:

    # A "Really? So she could have been my [persistent.mom]?"
    A "¿De verdad? ¿Así que ella podría haber sido mi [persistent.mom]?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:166
translate spanish a_convi_2_17788de7:

    # A "Really? So she could have been the one raising me instead?"
    A "¿De verdad? ¿Entonces podría haber sido ella quien me criara en su lugar?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:167
translate spanish a_convi_2_89ecc537:

    # A "That feels strange to me."
    A "Eso me resulta extraño."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:170
translate spanish a_convi_2_bca7266a:

    # Z "I don't know, [A]... I am not sure we would have worked out, in the end."
    Z "No sé, [A]... No estoy seguro de que hubiéramos funcionado, al final."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:171
translate spanish a_convi_2_51274e6b:

    # Z "I'm quite happy with [W], and would not have it any other way."
    Z "Soy muy feliz con [W], y no me gustaría que fuera de otra manera."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:174
translate spanish a_convi_2_36fc142d:

    # A "You really love her, don't you?"
    A "Realmente la amas, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:177
translate spanish a_convi_2_33f81c0c:

    # Z "What is there not to love? She is pretty, smart, loyal, and fiery."
    Z "¿Qué es lo que no hay que amar? Es bonita, inteligente, leal y fogosa."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:180
translate spanish a_convi_2_de3a9b7d:

    # A "I can be those things too!"
    A "¡Yo también puedo ser esas cosas!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:183
translate spanish a_convi_2_dd94ee8c:

    # Z "I know you can, [A]..."
    Z "Sé que puedes, [A]..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:186
translate spanish a_convi_2_9b3c056a:

    # A "Would you love me too, [persistent.dad]?"
    A "¿Tú también me querrías, [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:189
translate spanish a_convi_2_2ef726a4:

    # Z "You know I already do. And you know that I will always be there for you..."
    Z "Sabes que ya lo hago. Y sabes que siempre estaré a tu lado..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:192
translate spanish a_convi_2_6e20bd89:

    # A "Will I have to get married to someone too?"
    A "¿También tendré que casarme con alguien?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:197
translate spanish a_convi_2_51fca82c:

    # Z "I am not sure yet, but yes, this is the way, in Zeta, for most people."
    Z "Todavía no estoy seguro, pero sí, ese es el camino, en Zeta, para la mayoría de la gente."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:200
translate spanish a_convi_2_05f419dd:

    # A "What if I don't want to?"
    A "¿Y si no quiero?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:203
translate spanish a_convi_2_100dee78:

    # Z "Then you would have to find a way to fend for yourself. Do you think you would be able to?"
    Z "Entonces tendrías que encontrar la forma de valerte por ti misma. ¿Crees que serías capaz?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:206
translate spanish a_convi_2_2c4eef95:

    # A "I don't know, [persistent.dad]."
    A "No lo sé, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:209
translate spanish a_convi_2_a60ecd20:

    # Z "There you go then."
    Z "Ahí lo tienes entonces."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:212
translate spanish a_convi_2_1982e7fa:

    # A "This is stupid..."
    A "Esto es una estupidez..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:215
translate spanish a_convi_2_a80e5f62:

    # Z "You know that everybody, from the lowest of slaves to the Queen, has to do their part, don't you?"
    Z "Sabes que todo el mundo, desde el más bajo de los esclavos hasta la Reina, tiene que hacer su parte, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:218
translate spanish a_convi_2_427ff2be:

    # A "Sorry, [persistent.dad]. I will do better, I promise."
    A "Lo siento, [persistent.dad]. Lo haré mejor, lo prometo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:222
translate spanish a_convi_2_ae1f74eb:

    # Z "I like having you here with us."
    Z "Me gusta tenerte aquí con nosotros."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:223
translate spanish a_convi_2_8041ef16:

    # Z "That should answer your question."
    Z "Eso debería responder a tu pregunta."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:226
translate spanish a_convi_2_f4294716:

    # A "Yay... then we will talk no more about me being married to some horny kid."
    A "Viva... Entonces no hablaremos más de que estoy casada con un jovencito cachondo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:229
translate spanish a_convi_2_c0469a2f:

    # Z "Very true. Let's talk instead about you taking care of me and your [persistent.mom] until we are nothing more than dried husks and old bones."
    Z "Muy cierto. Hablemos, en cambio, de que tú te ocupes de mí y de tu [persistent.mom] hasta que no seamos más que cáscaras secas y huesos viejos."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:232
translate spanish a_convi_2_4e851743:

    # A "Ewww.... Why did you have to make it weird?"
    A "Eeee.... ¿Por qué has tenido que hacerlo tan raro?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:235
translate spanish a_convi_2_1e924b8b:

    # Z "We won't always be in the good shape you've known us to be, you know?"
    Z "No siempre estaremos en la buena forma que nos has conocido, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:238
translate spanish a_convi_2_0058e38e:

    # A "I am very happy to ignore what you just said!"
    A "¡Me alegra mucho ignorar lo que acabas de decir!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:242
translate spanish a_convi_2_38afa711:

    # Z "Don't you want a husband of your own?"
    Z "¿No quieres un marido propio?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:245
translate spanish a_convi_2_9323d700:

    # A "I don't know... I'm happy here."
    A "No sé... Soy feliz aquí."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:248
translate spanish a_convi_2_f22b22a2:

    # Z "I'm happy you are here too, but you might meet someone, some day; someone you like even more than you like being here."
    Z "Yo también me alegro de que estés aquí, pero puede que algún día conozcas a alguien; alguien que te guste incluso más que estar aquí."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:251
translate spanish a_convi_2_3122c1ae:

    # A "I don't know about that..."
    A "No sé yo..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:254
translate spanish a_convi_2_1d245b73:

    # Z "Neither do I, but if you do, you must promise to tell me."
    Z "Yo tampoco, pero si lo haces, debes prometerme que me lo dirás."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:257
translate spanish a_convi_2_70cf76a8:

    # A "So that you can beat him and chase him away?"
    A "¿Para poder vencerlo y ahuyentarlo?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:260
translate spanish a_convi_2_04138a22:

    # Z "You may want me to do that today, but maybe on that day, you will want to leave with him."
    Z "Puede que hoy quieras que lo haga, pero puede que ese día quieras irte con él."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:263
translate spanish a_convi_2_31af24a3:

    # A "Never!"
    A "¡Nunca!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:266
translate spanish a_convi_2_5410d00a:

    # Z "You don't know that, dear... Promise me you will tell me, alright?"
    Z "No lo sabes, querida... Prométeme que me lo dirás, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:269
translate spanish a_convi_2_34226df9:

    # A "I don't like this promise, but ok... I promise."
    A "No me gusta esa promesa, pero vale... Lo prometo."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:272
translate spanish a_convi_2_f4f46af5:

    # Z "When it happens, we will decide together, if this young man that comes looking for you is worthy to be your suitor."
    Z "Cuando pase, decidiremos juntos si ese joven que viene a buscarte es digno de ser tu pretendiente."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:275
translate spanish a_convi_2_37b082c7:

    # A "I bet he won't!"
    A "¡Apuesto a que no lo hará!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:278
translate spanish a_convi_2_76c8d225:

    # Z "Well.. if he should not be, we will chase him away together!"
    Z "Bueno... si no debe ser así, ¡Lo echaremos juntos!"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:284
translate spanish a_convi_2x_8417c1e6:

    # A "I love you [persistent.dad]."
    A "Te quiero [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:287
translate spanish a_convi_2x_cb6d25ea:

    # Z "I know..."
    Z "Lo sé..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:288
translate spanish a_convi_2x_25e7a319:

    # Z "So, [A], why this interest in Rabiah? Where does it come from?"
    Z "Entonces, [A], ¿por qué este interés en Rabiah? ¿De dónde viene?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:291
translate spanish a_convi_2x_dc3b1e56:

    # A "[persistent.mom!c] told me auntie might come visit soon, and I can't remember the last time I saw her."
    A "[persistent.mom!c] me dijo que la tía podría venir de visita pronto, y no recuerdo la última vez que la vi."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:294
translate spanish a_convi_2x_3cd58998:

    # Z "You're right. Now that I think about it, she has not been here for several years."
    Z "Tienes razón. Ahora que lo pienso, no ha estado aquí desde hace varios años."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:295
translate spanish a_convi_2x_0345ccad:

    # Z "You were very young the last time she came to visit."
    Z "Eras muy joven la última vez que vino de visita."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:298
translate spanish a_convi_2x_ba93d129:

    # A "Doesn't her family live in the city?"
    A "¿No vive su familia en la ciudad?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:301
translate spanish a_convi_2x_2a5b846c:

    # Z "Yes, they do now, but they have lived in a remote village for several years."
    Z "Sí, lo hacen ahora, pero llevan varios años viviendo en una aldea remota."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:304
translate spanish a_convi_2x_36339c72:

    # A "Should we not have met them when they got back to Zeta then? Why didn't we do that?"
    A "¿No deberíamos habernos reunido con ellos cuando volvieron a Zeta entonces? ¿Por qué no lo hicimos?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:307
translate spanish a_convi_2x_3d3163f1:

    # Z "That's a good question. One I have not thought about at all."
    Z "Es una buena pregunta. Una en la que no he pensado en absoluto."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:308
translate spanish a_convi_2x_6ce5ae03:

    # Z "I think there might have been a bit of bad blood between your [persistent.mom] and her sister, in the past; but that should be over and done with now."
    Z "Creo que puede que haya habido un poco de mala sangre entre tu [persistent.mom] y su hermana, en el pasado; pero eso ya debería estar superado."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:311
translate spanish a_convi_2x_920f2f9f:

    # A "Do you think it's because of the girlfriend thing?"
    A "¿Crees que es por el tema de la novia?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:314
translate spanish a_convi_2x_060260f4:

    # Z "That could be the reason, but if that's the case, we should let them sort it out between themselves, don't you think?"
    Z "Esa podría ser la razón, pero si es así, deberíamos dejar que lo solucionen entre ellas, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:317
translate spanish a_convi_2x_906ad4ea:

    # A "I kinda want to know..."
    A "La verdad es que quiero saberlo..."

# game/scripts/convis_ain.rpy:320
translate spanish a_convi_2x_db1dcc42:

    # Z "Young lady, you will not embarrass your [persistent.mom] in front of her older sister."
